  07 Oct 2011; Nathan Phillip Brink <binki@gentoo.org> grit-2.4.1.ebuild:
  Remove extraneous eval instead of just committing a new Manifest.

  06 Oct 2011; Nathan Phillip Brink <binki@gentoo.org> grit-2.4.1.ebuild:
  Take advantage of RUBY_S's github support.

